7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Rephrase.ai and Topaz Video AI share a solid foundation of core features including Batch Processing. Where Rephrase.ai pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Text To Video and Avatar Talking Head and Templates and Voice Over and Api Access, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Rephrase.ai holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 6/10, while Topaz Video AI scores 8/10 overall and 6/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Rephrase.ai offers a more budget-friendly entry point at Contact sales, compared to Topaz Video AI's starting price of $199 one-time. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
