b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Who Should Choose Which?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The ideal user for each platform differs considerably. Rephrase.ai is best suited for personalized marketing videos, sales outreach at scale, making it a strong choice if you fall into any of these categories. Topaz Video AI, meanwhile, shines for video upscaling professionals, restoring old footage, which means it may be the better pick if your needs align with those use cases.\n\nFounded in 2019, Rephrase.ai describes itself as \"Create personalized AI videos at scale.\" Topaz Video AI, established in 2019, positions itself as \"AI-powered video upscaling and enhancement.\" Both platforms have been in the market for a similar duration, giving each ample time to refine their offerings and build a loyal user base."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"verdict-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Our Verdict"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"After analyzing all the data, **Topaz Video AI** comes out slightly ahead in this comparison, thanks to higher user ratings (8.0 vs 7.0). However, this does not mean Rephrase.ai is a poor choice — far from it. Rephrase.ai excels in its own right, particularly for personalized marketing videos and sales outreach at scale.\n\nOur recommendation: if you value best-in-class upscaling quality, go with Topaz Video AI. If excellent personalization api matters more to you, Rephrase.ai is the way to go. Either way, both are solid platforms that have earned their place in the market."}]]}]
